dc_title_s: Public Elementary School Attendance Boundaries: Chicago, Illinois, SY 2017 - 2018
dc_description_s: Attendance boundaries for elementary schools in the Chicago Public Schools district for school year 2017-2018. Generally, all students in the applicable middle school grades who live within one of these boundaries may attend the school. To view or use these shapefiles, compression software, such as 7-Zip, and special GIS software, such as Google Earth or ArcGIS, are required.
